{"id":33019,"date":"2024-01-01T16:54:12","date_gmt":"2024-01-01T11:24:12","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/?p=33019"},"modified":"2024-11-13T12:34:42","modified_gmt":"2024-11-13T07:04:42","slug":"white-wardrobe-design-ideas","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/bedroom-interiors\/white-wardrobe-design-ideas\/","title":{"rendered":"7 Fabulous White Wardrobe Design Ideas For Your Bedroom"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p>Save time on finding the perfect wardrobe for your bedroom with these white wardrobe design ideas.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Kudos to you if you\u2019re looking for a white wardrobe design. Usually, Indian homeowners tend to shy away from most things white, as white items have the tendency to lose sheen quickly with regular use and over time. But here\u2019s what is not commonly known \u2014 with a variety of materials, finishes and colour combinations, you can make the most of white modular wardrobes without worrying about dirty wardrobe exteriors. Instead, you can focus on other factors like how big a wardrobe would you need to fit your possessions? Should it be a freestanding, angular, floor-to-wall or full wall wardrobe? What colour combination with white would you like, if any? If you think these questions just made wardrobe shopping more complicated than you first thought, don\u2019t worry. Take a look at our expert-approved design suggestions and we\u2019ll help you get <em>your <\/em>white colour wardrobe<strong> <\/strong>right.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\">\n<figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"458\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/a-wall-mounted-458x1024.jpg\" alt=\"Tips to keep in mind while looking for a wall-mounted dressing table\" class=\"wp-image-47467\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/a-wall-mounted-458x1024.jpg 458w, https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/a-wall-mounted-134x300.jpg 134w, https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/a-wall-mounted-768x1718.jpg 768w, https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/a-wall-mounted-687x1536.jpg 687w, https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/a-wall-mounted-915x2048.jpg 915w, https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/a-wall-mounted-150x336.jpg 150w, https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2023\/07\/a-wall-mounted.jpg 940w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 458px) 100vw, 458px\" \/><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Full Wall White Wardrobe Design<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Many homeowners look for extra space in their wardrobe. And full-size mirrors? Bring\u2019em on! Now, how about a wardrobe design that does both? A sleek, full wall plywood white wardrobe with sliding mirrors is definitely just what you need. The full wall wardrobe allows for ample and efficient storage with multiple shelves, drawers and hanging rods. A bonus is that the mirrors keep your bedroom bright and make it seem more spacious!<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/01164304\/full-wall-white-wardrobe-design.jpg\" alt=\"A full-sized white wardrobe design with sliding door mirrors allows for ample and efficient storage in bedroom\" class=\"wp-image-33024\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/01164304\/full-wall-white-wardrobe-design.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/01164304\/full-wall-white-wardrobe-design-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/01164304\/full-wall-white-wardrobe-design-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/01164304\/full-wall-white-wardrobe-design-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Live large with a full wall white wardrobe design<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Dreamy Blue And White Wardrobe Design<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>In the bedroom, blue and white wardrobe designs lend a dreamy vibe, especially for a kid\u2019s room. Make it more fun for them with a full-length mirror on one of the doors. The freestanding wardrobe with predominant blue and a pop of white can act as a piece of accent furniture in a mostly white room. With a customised cabinet cum bookshelf and an executive study unit, children will have all they need to chase their dreams in one place.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/01164244\/bedroom-blue-and-white-wardrobe-design.jpg\" alt=\"Blue and white kids' wardrobe with full-length mirror on one door.\" class=\"wp-image-33021\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/01164244\/bedroom-blue-and-white-wardrobe-design.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/01164244\/bedroom-blue-and-white-wardrobe-design-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/01164244\/bedroom-blue-and-white-wardrobe-design-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/01164244\/bedroom-blue-and-white-wardrobe-design-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">A blue and white wardrobe design for kid\u2019s room<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n<div class=\"mbgc-slide-caption\"><a href=\"#contactUsModal\" data-toggle=\"modal\"><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Get a Free Modular Kitchen Worth \u20b92 Lakhs with Your Home Interiors.\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/08\/08183703\/designcafe-offer-free-modular-kitchen-worth-2-lakhs.jpg \" \/><\/a><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Humble White Almirah Design<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Some of you may have a strong preference for a compact white almirah design. In that case, a simple plywood almirah should work fine. For added sheen, you can go for a lacquered glass or laminate finish almirah. And if you like, a simple white almirah design gives you the opportunity to experiment with colours in the rest of the room. For instance, this room features multi-coloured and multi-functional individual storage boxes under the bench by the window. The rug and the other decor items in the room also add vibrant pops.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/01164237\/a-humble-white-almirah-design.jpg\" alt=\"White almirah with a clean design finish in a kids' room\" class=\"wp-image-33020\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/01164237\/a-humble-white-almirah-design.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/01164237\/a-humble-white-almirah-design-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/01164237\/a-humble-white-almirah-design-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/01164237\/a-humble-white-almirah-design-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Go all-white for a compact almirah<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Also, check out <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/bedroom-interiors\/almirah-designs-for-indian-bedroom\/\">Almirah Designs For Indian Bedroom<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Bold Pink And White Wardrobe Design<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>In this wardrobe design, white is the primary colour. Yet, the wardrobe\u2019s high-gloss laminate finish pops the bold pink without it being too overwhelming. Notice how the dual shade <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/bedroom-interiors\/modular-wardrobe-designs\/\">modular wardrobe design<\/a> blends into the white open shelves on the side. This also helps maintain the balance between the colours. The bed\u2019s custom headboard and the floating study table too follow the same <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/guides\/bedroom-colour-combinations\/\">dual colour scheme<\/a> maintaining a uniform look for the entire room. Thus, pops of pink make the room fun without being overpowering while white plays a balancing act.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/01164251\/bold-pink-and-white-wardrobe-design.jpg\" alt=\"Bold pink and white wardrobe design-high-gloss laminate finished in the bedroom\" class=\"wp-image-33022\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/01164251\/bold-pink-and-white-wardrobe-design.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/01164251\/bold-pink-and-white-wardrobe-design-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/01164251\/bold-pink-and-white-wardrobe-design-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/01164251\/bold-pink-and-white-wardrobe-design-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Go for a high-gloss bold pink and white wardrobe<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">An Extravagant Modern White Wardrobe Design<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>If you have the luxury of a spacious room, consider going for a wide and multi-functional white colour wardrobe. Take inspiration from this 3-door white wardrobe design which features open shelves on either side plus overhead cabinets! The geometric detail gives the white wardrobe design an exquisitely sleek and modern look. It also ensures that the wardrobe section stands out from the other attached units. It\u2019s the perfect white wardrobe design that combines superior storage in an optimal space setting! A rule of thumb for a white colour wardrobe like this to stand out is to surround it with vibrant elements.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/01164311\/modern-white-colour-wardrobe.jpg\" alt=\"A modern white wardrobe with three doors and open shelves on both sides, an exquisitely sleek look\" class=\"wp-image-33025\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/01164311\/modern-white-colour-wardrobe.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/01164311\/modern-white-colour-wardrobe-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/01164311\/modern-white-colour-wardrobe-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/01164311\/modern-white-colour-wardrobe-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">A multi-functional white wardrobe design<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">A Playful Light Purple And White Wardrobe Design<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Setting up a purple-and-white-themed bedroom? Look for the biggest piece of furniture in the room to make the theme evident. For instance, in one of the <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/interior-design\/kids-bedroom-design\/\">children\u2019s bedrooms<\/a> that we designed, we chose to keep the freestanding, multi-purpose wardrobe in purple and white. We then extended the colour palette to other parts of the room. This purple and white wardrobe design extends into a corner study, making optimum use of the space. More importantly, this white wardrobe design keeps children\u2019s needs in mind and features open shelves and closed cabinets at different heights so that children can store their essentials conveniently.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/01164319\/playful-light-purple-and-white-wardrobe-design.jpg\" alt=\"A light purple and white wardrobe design attached to the study unit\" class=\"wp-image-33026\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/01164319\/playful-light-purple-and-white-wardrobe-design.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/01164319\/playful-light-purple-and-white-wardrobe-design-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/01164319\/playful-light-purple-and-white-wardrobe-design-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/01164319\/playful-light-purple-and-white-wardrobe-design-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">Multi-purpose purple and white wardrobe design<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\"><strong>Tidy Up With Glossy Grey And White Wardrobe Designs<\/strong><\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>A wardrobe with ample storage space and compartments is a total dream. This grey and white wardrobe design is a perfect choice to fulfil your extra storage dreams. Even better, the multi-functional design features a pull-out desk to give you a corner study set up in no time! The compartments by the study table can double up as cabinets for the study unit along with the open shelves below. You can customise the size of the various cabinets, drawers and shelves in this modular wardrobe design to meet your specific needs.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><img decoding=\"async\" width=\"940\" height=\"564\" src=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/01164326\/tidy-up-with-glossy-grey-and-white-wardrobe-design.jpg\" alt=\"A grey and white wardrobe design glossy finish with a pull-out desk\" class=\"wp-image-33027\" srcset=\"https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/01164326\/tidy-up-with-glossy-grey-and-white-wardrobe-design.jpg 940w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/01164326\/tidy-up-with-glossy-grey-and-white-wardrobe-design-300x180.jpg 300w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/01164326\/tidy-up-with-glossy-grey-and-white-wardrobe-design-768x461.jpg 768w, https:\/\/media.designcafe.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/01164326\/tidy-up-with-glossy-grey-and-white-wardrobe-design-150x90.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 940px) 100vw, 940px\" \/><figcaption class=\"wp-element-caption\">A grey and white wardrobe design with lots of storage<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>We\u2019re sure it now seems relatively easier to decide on a white wardrobe design. If you like any of them already, go ahead and meet our designers to make it yours. If you have an idea for your kinda white wardrobe design, consult our designers today! We\u2019d love to customise it to your needs and <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/interior-design\/\">home interiors<\/a>. If you want to read up more on the different types of wardrobes, <a href=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/blog\/home-interiors\/types-of-wardrobe\/\">check this out<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"row blog-form\">\n\t<div class=\"offset-lg-3 col-lg-6 bg-light\">\n<fieldset class=\"field-set\">\n<!-- <legend align=\"left\"> -->\n                    \n    <h3 class=\"widget-title text-dark text-center mb-0\">Unwind In Your Personal Sanctuary<\/h3>\n  \n \n     <p class=\"text-center text-dark mt-0\"> Get 20% extra space with modular interiors<\/p>\n    <!-- <\/legend> -->\n<form id=\"blogContactUsFormMain\" action=\"https:\/\/www.designcafe.com\/get_qu